      "para_id": "Q001446.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninura , the mother of Umma , Nammahni , the governor of Umma built and restored her E-ula ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001446.9",
      "line_range": "9",
      "translation": "(9) At that time Yarlagan was the king of Gutium ."
    }
  ],
